<https://catalog.skara.se/store/1/resource/37> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page> <https://lankadedata.se/spec/lediga-tomter/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <https://catalog.skara.se/store/1/resource/37>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__910.
_:b0__910 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/owner>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2120001702>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://catalog.skara.se/store/1/resource/37> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Beskriver ledig tomtmark och i viss fall byggklara tomter för villor, bostadshus, industri och kommersiell verksamhet som finns tillgänglig för köp av Skara kommun. \n\nDatamängden innehåller flera distributioner där CSV-distributionen är den som utvärderar korrekt mot CSV-schema i specifikationen. Utöver detta har Skara kommun valt att distribuera flödande data direkt från kartsystem som GeoJSON, samt en JSON genererad från CSV men med tillägget att den innehåller ytbeskrivning i form av Polygon i SWEREF99:1330."@sv, "Describes vacant land and in some cases building-ready plots for villas, residential buildings, industry and commercial activities that are available for purchase by Skara municipality. \n\nThe dataset contains several distributions where the CSV distribution is the one that evaluates correctly against the CSV schema in the specification. In addition to this, Skara municipality has chosen to distribute flowing data directly from gis-system as GeoJSON, as well as a JSON generated from CSV but with the addition that it contains surface description in the form of Polygon in SWEREF99:1330."@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <https://sws.geonames.org/2678205>, _:b0__7738.
_:b0__7738 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((13.16 58.46,13.76 58.46,13.76 58.275,13.16 58.275,13.16 58.46))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://catalog.skara.se/store/1/resource/37> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://catalog.skara.se/store/1/resource/62>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#version> "1";
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://www.skara.se/byggaboochmiljo/levaochboiskarakommun/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-17T09:06:00.000Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://dataportal.se/specifications/ledigatomter/2.0>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "mark"@sv, "fastigheter"@sv, "property"@en, "villa"@en, "land"@en, "plots"@en, "villa"@sv, "tomt"@sv, "tomtkö"@sv, "lots"@en, "queue"@en, "area"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/AS_NEEDED>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "ledig-tomtmark", "available-plots";
