<#a45fc0748c8ffac7a42dc0cd25c28701> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/75076d38-25e6-4ad6-9cb9-878708728f93>;
