    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2026-03-18"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "1995-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>, <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/762376b4-1f11-4d40-a4c6-865c98ae3765> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__24019.
