<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/bf657f00-2e98-11ed-84f0-5b3e6bab28c1> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__48173.
_:b0__48173 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((10.00 70.00,25.00 70.00,25.00 55.00,10.00 55.00,10.00 70.00))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
