_:b0__948 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: Folkhälsomyndigheten (HLV)"@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U01429> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-12-16"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
