    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE5564795598>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This repository contains the MicroVision dataset: anonymized images and annotations of vulnerable road users and micromobility vehicles in real traffic (pedestrians, bicycles, cyclists, e-scooters, and e-scooterists). We further provide some first benchmark object-detection model weights (YOLO11, Faster R-CNN, and RF-DETR)."@en, "Det här arkivet innehåller MicroVision-datasetet: anonymiserade bilder och annoteringar av utsatta trafikanter och mikromobilitetsfordon i verklig trafik (fotgängare, cyklar, cyklister, elscootrar och elscooterförare). Vi tillhandahåller dessutom några första benchmark-vikter för objektigenkänningsmodeller (YOLO11, Faster R-CNN och RF-DETR)."@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://sws.geonames.org/2711533>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/72d5f84d5028bed1fe0e99aa3e1918ac>, <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/e87571585e12ba3cff852c19878c33c4>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.71870/eepz-jd52#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2026-03-16T13:55:08.74184Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.71870/eepz-jd52>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-16T13:55:08.74184Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "MicroVision dataset"@en, "MicroVision dataset"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TECH>;
