<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#b4d7b25319aedf841130621a2d8aa7ce>.
<#b4d7b25319aedf841130621a2d8aa7ce> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/002644>;
