<https://doi.org/10.5878/002809> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#8796efec54388cdc9e5ed123cdc064b3>.
<#8796efec54388cdc9e5ed123cdc064b3> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
