<#cfe03ac8cb8ad0610edf92c400a59849> {
<https://www.geodata.se/resources/2905b7b7-be1d-45d5-9f62-9278680eb4f2> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Inspire"@sv, "Naturliga riskområden"@sv;
